com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.china.constants

注释类型 ChinaStyle.ChinaStyleVersion


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public static @interface ChinaStyle.ChinaStyleVersion
    Indicates the which style version numbers are acceptable as method parameters. Using one of these constants enables the retrieval of a certain version of a Chinese map style. Map style design may change as we improve the styles.
    从以下版本开始:
    0.4.7
